    rdfs:comment "A central node in C2, with symmetric relations to other C2 nodes and a link to the super node." ;
    sc:R9 sc:E138, sc:E139 ;
    sc:R1 sc:E100 ;
    sc:R10 sc:E140 .

# --- Hub Node (C5) ---
